2個目は記述が少ない
範囲演算子 n..m
sumメソッド　　sum = (n..m).sum

def sum_number(n, m)  
  start = n
  ss = 0
  while start <= m
    ss += start
    start += 1
  end
   puts ss
end
sum_number(5,15)

-----------------------
def sum_number(n, m)
  sum = (n..m).sum
  puts sum
end
sum_number(5, 15)
-----------------------

def sum_number(n, m)
  total = 0 
  while n <= m 
    total = total + n 
    n = n + 1
  end
  puts total
end
sum_number(5, 15)
----------------------
